/lileks.com/mpls/daytons/index.html">Dayton's Department Store</a>, and the kitchen of the celebrated <a href="http://www.yelp.com/biz/red-lobster-golden-valley">Red Lobster of Golden Valley</a>.</p><p>Current + evergreen obsessions:</p><ul><li>Cities, architecture, urbanism, transit, civic tech, economic opportunity, and sustainability.</li><li>The Internet, tech, artificial intelligence and machine learning, startups, consumer and SaaS product design, the media industry, business strategy, and global scaling.</li><li>Public policy, constitutional law, free speech, privacy, rule of law, and democratic vitality.</li><li>Progressive politics, political theory and philosophy, American and world history.</li><li>Books, bikes, beagles.</li></ul>]]></content:encoded></item><item><title><![CDATA[James Vasile]]></title><description><![CDATA[James Vasile [https://startpage.com/?query=james%20vasile] has over twenty years
