0000127538a</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Claire Olmstead]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Wed, 09 Jun 2021 19:09:39 GMT</pubDate><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>Using the DSNP SDK, the Example Client demonstrates how to quickly integrate with the DSNP and manage all three elements.</p>]]></content:encoded></item><item><title><![CDATA[What We Do]]></title><description><![CDATA[DSNP.org is an independent non-profit organization, focused on the Decentralized
